@startuml
title Séquence – Actions clés sur index.html
actor User

User -> Sidebar: Clique "Mes guides"
Sidebar --> Main: Affiche section "Mes guides"

User -> Main: Clique "Nouveau guide" (btnNew)
Main -> Backend: POST /guides (nouveau)
Backend --> Main: 201 + redirect /guides/:id
Main --> User: Éditeur de guide affiché

User -> Main: Recherche "demo"
Main -> Backend: GET /guides?q=demo
Backend --> Main: JSON { items: [...] }
Main --> User: Liste filtrée

@enduml
